{
  "stem": "24195.6",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he even found me a place in the summer time, which is very hard in-- to get in Atlantic City back in the '50s, when it was in the world's playground, before casinos and everything.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a nice place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he found me a job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I start-- I said, don't you, don't you, don't you worry about me when I'm sitting on the rewrite desk and people from the public call in, and I'm answering, and I have an accent?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, forget.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I, I always thought people that were educated in Europe have a better education than, than we have in the US, which is not, not true any more, you know?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was true in those days, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I had no qualms to and, and worries that I couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he-- in fact, the first day I reported to work, he walks me over from his office to the main news desk where all the editors are sitting.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he says to me, as we walk there, he says, what name do you go by, he says.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said, gee, I, I go-- my name is Ludwig or Ludwig Joseph.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He says, well, he says, for some reason, it sounds a little-- not strange.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know what word he used.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But he says it doesn't just sound catchy enough.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He says, what is the English translation of, of Ludwig?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I said, I believe it's Louis-- L-O-U-I-S.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He says, why don't you call yourself Lou?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He gave me my name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] And is that where--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, so that nobody-- yeah, and most of the people in [INAUDIBLE], including my family, everybody knows me as Lou.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I, I accept that very much.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
